{"tid":1739010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(香港民意) 本土港產片 不敵「奶共合拍片」","createTime":"2019-11-19T12:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:55:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3e637e942827348c47aa38ad6efd32d307ee89","tid":1739010,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"香港票房, 可以話係一場選舉 : 香港人用自己既金錢, 購票顯示民意<br />\n結果, 《失蹤》和《獅子山上》兩套真本土港產片, 票房都大敗比奶共合拍片《催眠．裁決》...<br />\n<br />\n《獅子山上》 - 《十年》發行商Golden Scene投資兼發行既本土港產片.<br />\n《失蹤》 - 唔只係本土港產片. 套片既原著作家孔明, 直情係非常支持抗爭手足.<br />\n<br />\n《催眠．裁決》 - 大陸小鮮肉張翰主演, 講述前大陸特種部隊隊員 大發神威救人.<br />\n<br />\n結果, 《催眠．裁決》既單日票房大勝《失蹤》和《獅子山上》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F72090&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=1e1794b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72090</a><br />\n<br />\n中型發行的港片方面，兩部新開畫新晉導演執導的港片周末於28院映約70場下，均錄得逾一倍二的爬升。當中Screen Media、趙羅尼執導的《失蹤》錄得近千七人次，每場平均人次達24，推算收入接近12萬，三天累積約26萬。而高先發行、梁國斌執導的《獅子山上》在人次與推算收入則為《失蹤》一半，不過三天連同早前優先場下，累積仍接近30萬。......<br />\n<br />\n三部上周開畫電影仍在十大之內，當中美亞發行，黎兆鈞、施柏林與劉永泰合導的《催眠．裁決》在周末維持於47院映近百一場錄得近5,300人次，爬升達一倍三，每場平均人次接近50，推算收入在35萬以上，看來電影題材仍能吸引觀眾，可望於今天上映第11天累積達四百萬。"},{"pid":"5d09dc70abd9eaf37ad961e57e216a5e353f713a","tid":1739010,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"而家, 全世界都興本土電影熱潮<br />\nHollywood電影既外國票房都不斷下降 （只有迪士尼/Marvel電影的海外票房繼續上升，其他公司既海外票房都下滑緊。佢地都好驚）<br />\n<br />\n香港係小數例外, 其實好可惜.... (新一集Terminator差唔多係全世界都仆直, 但係香港依然大收)"},{"pid":"d714b00e3fd907c02045abe99034f478ecec2380","tid":1739010,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7c35cfb755bfb0d72182d7fb079714aebaa4f7","tid":1739010,"uid":103678,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢仲有心情睇戲既<br />\n唔覺佢地會欣賞港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40f741d9c376f5780eab54d095f39506c00b728","tid":1739010,"uid":108073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"仲有心情睇戲既係咩人 咪咩結果囉"},{"pid":"986004b3ff02f2b567cbf3829e95b0116a49b5ba","tid":1739010,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e7c35cfb755bfb0d72182d7fb079714aebaa4f7","tid":1739010,"uid":103678,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢仲有心情睇戲既<br />\n唔覺佢地會欣賞港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09ca419223ea70274e486b5429e9c197abff3e4","tid":1739010,"uid":32416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢仲去睇戲嘅會係咩人？"},{"pid":"47ca7a0a86b7eeb98228d8b3cd04e94025311b29","tid":1739010,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"看下有無時間幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ee81c5af1dc65150dda740bc5a71eee1bba7fb","tid":1739010,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"350d6ef87bf845f0ab1e37e8b25cb4143dadf96f","tid":1739010,"uid":52590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好講港產片，我有幾套外國戲好想睇都冇心情睇啦"},{"pid":"295c529b0a2d0a4b5000abbd4b52c879d2b4c979","tid":1739010,"uid":76922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"Joker 至今都冇心情睇"},{"pid":"acdcd0f2b8244826512f30d5b0e77c347a1f7b08","tid":1739010,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12